Package: ggbond
Title: Interactive Layout Editor for R Plots
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "BeiHao",
        family = "Li",
        role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        email = "szright2000@gmail.com"
    )
Description: Provides a Shiny-based layout editor for arranging R plot objects
    on a fixed-size canvas. It supports 'ggplot2' plots, base graphics functions
    and recorded plots, 'pheatmap' objects, 'ComplexHeatmap' objects, grid grobs,
    'gtables', and local raster images, with live preview and PDF or PNG export.
